name: I Don't Like It! After Beuys
description:
Snoopy believes that everyone is an artist, However, Garfield does not want to be an artist. 
"Why should everyone be an artist?" ask Garfield. Garfield wants to ignore snoopy and he just want to sleep. This event remind us of the iconic Joseph Beuys' Performance piece, titled "I Like America and America Likes Me, in 1974.
